Pre-Game Insights: Netherlands have been one of the most tactically astute teams in the tournament, even if they haven't quite put together all facets of their game yet.
England have performed well below expectations but will probably still start as favourites.
Miscellaneous Highlights: England and Netherlands have faced off on 6 occasions in ODIs, with England winning all 6 times.
The match will begin at 2:00pm IST.

The match will be streamed on Star Sports/Disney+ Hotstar in India, Fox Cricket/9Now, Kayo Sports in Australia, Sky Sports/Sky Sports Go, Now TV in UK, Sky Sport/Sky Sport Now in New Zealand, and Willow TV/ESPN+ in USA/Canada.
Others: Netherlands will be looking to win a third match and cement qualification for the 2025 Champions Trophy.
